Quickstrike:







Quickstrike leaned up fast, getting nervous between the argument. A little 
too fast. His head rushed from the movement. "Shut up!" he yelled. "Shut up! 
Shredder, sit down!" He wasn't in the mood. He turned his head to him. 
"Maybe he's gotta right." He turned his head to Sinesis. "Ya want t' know 
these tin-horn's names? That all ya want?" He really wasn't feeling good. A 
few seconds, later, he felt like he would pass out. Now he knew he was 
posioned.
